txt.en: Head into the Ettenmoors and collect the materials that are needed to reinforce the gate at Tírith Rhaw.
'The material is not going to crawl to us. You need to get out there and collect it: wood, iron, and lashing. Go!'
You are directed back into the wilds of the Ettenmoors to collect material needed to reinforce the gate at Tírith Rhaw.

'Listen up, whelp! The Free People will not relent. They will return with rams and forces to retake this tower. We must be prepared.\n\n'Go back into the wilds and get more material to reinforce the gate we have built. We will not let this tower fall back into the hands of the enemy!'
Deliver the materials to Gaath at Tiríth Rhaw
'Good work. With this we can make the gate stronger. It will not survive forever, but we stand a better chance because of your effort.\n\n'Take this, you deserve it.'
Defence: Reinforce the Gate at Tiríth Rhaw
